It is indeed a &quot;puff&quot;. But it does contain some useful info indicating where
all the present fuss stems from and why.

From my reading of the article, the current situation has arisen from the
fact that the scientist caveats, reservations etc contained in the body of
the IPCC reports were excluded from the summaries. Politicians and others
didn't read beyond the summary and so that became &quot;Gospel&quot;. Thus we now have
Global Warming whereas some thirty years ago we had Global Cooling. I'm not
a climatologist, but AFAIK the Earth's climate doesn't change that quickly.

Youthful idealists don't usually have a memory of events before they were
born, so they won't know about the Global Cooling scare and have picked up
on the current panic. Give it a few years and something else will come along
to feed people's paranoia.
